<h2>New Session Request from {{menteeName}}</h2>

<p>Hello {{mentorName}},</p>

<p>Great news! You have a new mentorship session request.</p>

<div class='info-box'>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Mentee:</strong> {{menteeName}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Scheduled Time:</strong> {{scheduledTime}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
  {{#if sessionType}}
    <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Session Type:</strong> {{sessionType}}</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

{{#if description}}
  <h3>Session Details:</h3>
  <p>{{description}}</p>
{{/if}}

<p style='text-align: center;'>
  <a href='{{appUrl}}' class='button'>Review Request in App</a>
</p>

<p>You can review this request and accept or decline it in the Spiriment app. The mentee is waiting for your response!</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  <strong>What's Next?</strong><br/>
  • Open the Spiriment app<br/>
  • Go to the "Sessions" tab<br/>
  • Review the request in the "Pending" section<br/>
  • Accept or decline the session
</p>

<p>Thank you for your dedication to mentoring and helping others grow in their faith journey.</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  Blessings,<br/>
  <strong style='color: #3A5A40;'>The Spiriment Team</strong>
</p>
